Package: libegl-vivante1
Section: libs
Architecture: arm64
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libgal-vivante1 (=6.4.0.p2.4-1), libdrm-vivante1, libgbm-vivante1 (=6.4.0.p2.4-1), libc6
Provides: libegl1
Conflicts: libegl1
Replaces: libegl1
Description: libEGL
 Implementation of EGL API for Vivante GPU
 This package contains the EGL native platform graphics interface library.
 EGL provides a platform-agnostic mechanism for creating rendering surfaces
 for use with other graphics libraries, such as OpenGL|ES.
 .
 This package contains the Mesa vendor library for EGL.
 Implementation of EGL API for Vivante GPU

